      Create a new Report instance
      Parameters:

      teacher - The Teacher responsible for grading the project/assignment
      student - The student whose work is being assessed
      annotatedClasses - A set of class objects having a given annotation
      annotatedMethods - A set of methods having a given annotation
      annotatedFields - A set of fields having the given annotation
      overallGrade - The overall grade being awarded to the student
